			<div class="content" id="post-content-2464866">
									

<p>SO, last year, somebody thought that the influx of March Madness tales was going to be a lot bigger than it actually was, and created a <a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/marchmadness">sandbox page</a> for them. There were a lot of positive comments, a lot of good ideas, and then only one dingus ever actually used the damn thing.</p>
<p>This year, though, we start early. One huge collaboration, with as many rounds documented as possible.</p>
<p>The rules are on the page.</p>

