														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2464431">
									

<p>Hm&#8230; we've never really seen the Republic go all out in a fight. We don't know how big it's Department of Defense might be, and it apparently can't get hurt until a declaration of war is given. This would give it time to mobilize. Overall, it's probably not going to win, but depending on its forces it could make it pretty far up.</p>
<p>Further predictions</p>
<p>Tree rats would probably actually get recruited by the Sciurine Crusaders.</p>
<p>The Gorilla is strong, but its only really effective against biologically based opponents, so it will probably fall once it reaches any of the robotic foes, of which we have plenty.</p>
<p>It's bleeding song will lose once it fight someone or something which can't hear/entity which does not have eardrums to hear.</p>
<p>Not sure how maximum baseball league will play out, but I'm excited.</p>

							</div>

								
					
